MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

96-937. In re Cash.

Madison County, No. CA96-02-007. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Madison County. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
